title: Fist Fights: why I do push-ups (on my knuckles) every day.
description: Peace is the shadow of war.  Peace, order and good government are all created by fear, enforcement, and an awareness of the danger (though not the difficulty) of breaking the laws that govern our daily life.  Real talk.  And, yeah, some guy tried to start a fight with me on a bus in Victoria.  :-/
